name: Cuttin' Scissors! (Stickers)
description:
Bust out these giant scissors during a pre-season game for maximum taunting ability! Anytime a opposing player drops a ball, fumbles, or does anything you deem to be worth of being cut, bring our the Scissors and make sure the oppositions coach knows how much his players suck!

These are High Quality 32" vinyl stickers, apply to cardboard, cut out and go!

Order includes 4 stickers (Side A Front/Back and Side B Front/back) and assembly instructions.

Order by Wednesday June 9th to recieve your scissors in time for the June 13th Pre-Season game!

Pick up Friday June 9th at FloPrint.com on 1785 Albert St.
